<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Dating sims (or dating simulations) are a video game subgenre of simulation games, usually Japanese, with romantic elements. They are also sometimes put under the category of neoromance. The most common objective of dating sims is to date, usually choosing from among several characters, and to achieve a romantic relationship. The term dating sim is also often used as a synonym for the visual novel genre. However, this is mixing genre and medium, as visual novels are considered a subgenre of adventure games and the term does not cover simulations. While the two genres often share a common visual presentation, dating sims are sometimes considered to be more statistically based than the "choose your own adventure" style of visual novels.
                  <br><br>Simple 1500 Series Vol.081 - The Renai Adventure - Okaeri! is a dating first person adventure game that was also released for the Sega Dreamcast console.
                  <br><br>Tutoring is tough work and over the course of 4 weeks, as a teacher that returns home and will have to help 5 girls to study and prepare for an exam. Whilst in the throes of studious ardor, you may find some of your pupils appealing and put the virtual moves on her... them...
                  <br><br>The game features japanese voice acting for all the characters and an unlockable picture gallery that will be unlocked playing the adventure.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>The alternative scenario to occur with a branching story progresses, the adventure story full voice served a variety of birth. The hero comes back to his native princess Kamishima educational practice, such as a beautiful girl and childhood friend has grown in Noriawaseta ferry, with five daughters to spend four weeks teaching practice ....
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>First person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Dating, Romance & Anime themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

